<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich VI., Graf von Görz</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die gewährte Zollfreiheit für Nürnberger Bürger und Kaufleute und bittet um Fürsprache bei Johann Meinhard, Graf von Görz und Bruder Heinrichs, um Gewährung des gleichen Privilegs.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_55" id="26r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_55_r1l33">Dem Hochgeporen 
<del rend="strikethrough">H </del> herren / <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>heinrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Grafen cʒu Görcʒ etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_55_r1l35">Gnedıger 
<add><ab facs="#facs_55_r1l34"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> v̈mb </del> <expan>ſölch<ex>er</ex></expan> brief vnd freẏheit / damit Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_55_line_1574238069173_650"> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger vnd kauffleute / 
<del rend="strikethrough">mıt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_55_line_1574238072548_655">vnd auch </ab></add> <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> habe vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_55_r1l38">kauffmanſchaft durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_55_line_1574238075939_660">lande </ab></add> herſchaft vnd gepiete </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_55_r1l39"><expan>ſich<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu varen cʒu wandeln vnd cʒu <expan>arbeite<ex>n</ex></expan> / begnadet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_55_r1l40">vnd gefreẏet habt / <expan>Dancke<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_55_r1l41">fleiſʒ / vnd <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hochwirdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>fleiſʒıklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_55_r1l42">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> dinſt <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></del> / <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> pruder Graf hanſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_55_r1l44">von Görcʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_55_r1l43"><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ernſtlıch </del> biten 
<del rend="strikethrough"> w </del> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_55_r1l45">
<del rend="strikethrough">fürdrer </del> <expan>B<ex>urgern</ex></expan> vnd kauffleute <expan>gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> fürderer gen Jm ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_55_r1l46">wöllet / daʒ Jre 
<del rend="strikethrough">des </del> von ſeinen gnaden auch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_55_line_1574238370966_692">mit </ab></add> <expan>ſolche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>briefe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_56" id="26v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_56_r1l4"> <expan>freẏheite<ex>n</ex></expan> begnadet vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">gefreyet </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_56_r1l2"><expan>fürſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> als d </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_56_line_1574238451927_715">daʒ ſıe </ab></add> ſicher <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_56_line_1574238461548_720">lande herſchaft vnd gepiete 
<del rend="strikethrough"> cʒu varen cʒu </del> wandeln vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_56_r1l7">
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu </del> <expan>arbeıte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_56_line_1574238465177_725">mugen </ab></add> als ſie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden gefreyet vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_56_r1l8">begnadet ſein / das wöllen etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_55" id="26r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem hochgeporen herren, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, grafen czu Görcz etc. </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <add><expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan></add>,
                            <expan>sölch<ex>er</ex></expan> brief und freyheit, damit ir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger und kauffleute <add>und
                            auch</add>
<expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> habe und kauffmanschaft durch
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add>lande</add>, herschaft und gepiete <expan>sich<ex>er</ex></expan> czu
                        varen, czu wandeln und czu <expan>arbeite<ex>n</ex></expan> begnadet und
                        gefreyet habt, <expan>dancke<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz
                        und <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hochwirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleisziklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        pruder, graf Hansen von Görcz, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <add><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add> biten und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> und kauffleute
                            <expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> fürderer gen im sein wöllet, daz ire
                        von seinen gnaden auch <add>mit</add>
<expan>solche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>briefe<ex>n</ex></expan> und <pb facs="#facs_56" id="26v"/>
<expan>freyheite<ex>n</ex></expan> begnadet und
                                <add><expan>fürseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>
<expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>, <add>daz sie</add> sicher
                                <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> sein lande, herschaft und gepiete
                        wandeln und <expan>arbeite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>mugen</add>, als sie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden gefreyet und begnadet sein. Das
                        wöllen etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
